{
  "stem": "10406.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a car that was almost like a limo, except the military-- a military version, that must have brought in a very high-ranking officer that was there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once the people were lined up there, they couldn't get away, and they were already watched with machine guns.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I got scared.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I saw that, I somehow-- you know, the atmosphere was very frightening.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got out of there, and then I noticed they marched-- they marched those people to the German headquarters.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then later on, I heard shots coming from that area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Germans later-- some people were let go that had specific crafts, specific type of workers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Later, the Germans let it be known that those people were taken away for labor, to a labor camp, and that within a year, they're going to return.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "To me it was obvious what was happening there when I heard the shots.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Later on, I saw Ukrainian men going through the back, through, like, the meadow area with shovels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Some of the mothers and wives and sisters chose to believe that that was true-- that they-- they them for work and that they're going to come back.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "In 1993 when I went back to put up monuments in the town, one of the monuments we put up was for these 400 men that were shot on that day.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then that-- you know, that happened and it was over with.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then the SS disappeared from town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, everybody was still home at that point.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only the men that left left, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the families, all the families, and the children they didn't bother at that point and the women they didn't bother at that point.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
